{"tid":2398280,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［數學問題］三元一次方程組","createTime":"2021-02-07T07:07:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-17T18:47:40.000Z","uid":337498,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"953ef211f425c39e8d55e0035039e7a88575bf88","tid":2398280,"uid":337498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T07:07:14.000Z","msg":"對任意三元一次方程組，其解為<br />\n(X,Y,Z)=(a,b,c)現令<br />\n(X,Y,Z)=(yz,xz,xy)=(a,b,c)<br />\n求(x,y,z)。<br />\n<br />\n方法一：<br />\nxyz=xX=yY=zZ=ax=by=cz<br />\n建立一個三元一次方程組<br />\nax-by=0<br />\nax-cz=0<br />\nby-cz=0<br />\n這是一條齊次方程式，其解為<br />\n(0,0,0)或((ab)t,(ac)t,(bc)t)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n方法二：<br />\n(xyz)&sup2;=XYZ<br />\nxyz=&radic;(XYZ)=&radic;(abc)<br />\nx=xyz/X<br />\ny=xyz/Y<br />\nz=xyz/Z<br />\n則(x,y,z)=(&radic;(bc/a),&radic;(ac/b),&radic;(ab/c))<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實，方法二是官方答案。但問題是為何方法一會證明出，所有三元一次方程都存在一個解，即(0,0,0)。亦即是所有三元一次方程都是齊次方程。<br />\n希望各位數神幫手望望，睇下我方法一到底錯邊度。麻煩各位。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n注：(0,0,0)=(x,y,z)<br />\n(X,Y,Z)=(yz,xz,xy)=(0,0,0)"},{"pid":"2c469572d10afb81d7b4e9d2af48dbd46432c071","tid":2398280,"uid":196924,"like":16,"dislike":4,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T07:19:07.000Z","msg":"呢啲用中文真係完全睇唔撚明"},{"pid":"b4375a6eae7b009e6e7ac7e2fee3aef75cc70659","tid":2398280,"uid":55011,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2c469572d10afb81d7b4e9d2af48dbd46432c071","tid":2398280,"uid":196924,"like":16,"dislike":4,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T07:19:07.000Z","msg":"呢啲用中文真係完全睇唔撚明"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T07:29:05.000Z","msg":"中文完全唔明+1<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2c1e22d0f6d4512a6d1599fe00da91b53aa305c","tid":2398280,"uid":5725,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-07T07:30:20.000Z","msg":"題目冇俾哂constraints 出黎掛<br />\n但佢開方又唔加正負<br />\n<br />\n不過可能係佢講明三元一次, 所以定義上a,b,c 都唔會係0<br />\n同埋大楷XYZ都唔知寫出黎做乜尻"},{"pid":"09b05ca326250ce043